column5: Hey,  So I got bored and made a youtube video about spring pike fishing with minnow baits...check it out if you're as bored as I was!    P.S. I think I stole like 10 peoples Username's lol  -Ben
OMG!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!  Unabomber made a fishing video   :lol:  :lol:  Just kidding!!!!!!!!!!
Thats what I was going for!! seriously, gotta keep my identity secret!  -Ben
I felt like I was getting nautious watching the video. Hold the baits still for a second. Keep moving them around causes a blur (or maybe I'm having a stroke).
Ben, that was fun, but what, you have a big poker game to play or something?
yep...you were definatly bored...and now i am too...lol....j/k
